trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlDocument" /> class is an abstract class to construct or manipulate a DSML document.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlDocument" /> 類別是用來建構和操作 DSML 文件的抽象類別，

trans-unit.source: It is the base class for both <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlRequestDocument" /> and <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlResponseDocument" />.
trans-unit.target: 它是 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlRequestDocument" /> 和 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlResponseDocument" /> 的基底類別。

trans-unit.source: Each item in its collection is an object derived from <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryOperation" />.
trans-unit.target: 其集合中的每個項目都是衍生自 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryOperation" /> 的物件。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlDocument.#ctor" /> constructor creates an instance of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlDocument" /> class.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlDocument.#ctor" /> 建構函式會建立 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlDocument" /> 類別的執行個體。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlDocument.ToXml" /> method transforms this <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlDocument" /> object into a <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlDocument" /> object.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlDocument.ToXml" /> 方法會將這個 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlDocument" /> 物件變換為 <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlDocument" /> 物件。
經過轉換的 <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlDocument" /> 物件。
